                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> The prisoner went by the name of Joseph Vardon in my service—this is my waistcoat—I have worn it—it was made in my shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined Q.</hi> How long had the prisoner lived with you? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About nine months—he was employed by my predecessor—I believe he deserved a good a character.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
